5. Deployment Commands
bash
# Single server deployment
chmod +x deploy.sh
./deploy.sh

# Docker deployment
npm run docker:build
npm run docker:run

# Multi-region deployment (run on each server)
scp deploy.sh user@server:/tmp/
ssh user@server "bash /tmp/deploy.sh"
